Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:19.03,Translation,,0,0,0,,The orbs scattered all over this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:22.20,Translation,,0,0,0,,Those not captured by sight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:26.24,Translation,,0,0,0,,The observer without a form
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:28.51,Translation,,0,0,0,,attains omniscience
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:31.28,Translation,,0,0,0,,A repeating pendulum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:35.51,Translation,,0,0,0,,A motive just slightly impure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:41.62,Translation,,0,0,0,,The fruit of the tree of life has fallen to the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:48.29,Translation,,0,0,0,,If this maniacal ritual, mysterious like magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:54.07,Translation,,0,0,0,,can succeed with the stroke of a brush drawing a magic circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:57.80,Translation,,0,0,0,,I will deny the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:58.77,Translation,,0,0,0,,Illuminato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:04.21,Translation,,0,0,0,,As if “it” sees through everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:08.18,Translation,,0,0,0,,it sneers with its reprehensible power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.92,Translation,,0,0,0,,as it fills with bliss
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.05,Translation,,0,0,0,,Illuminato
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:17.42,Translation,,0,0,0,,The more it “flaunts” entangled depictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:21.63,Translation,,0,0,0,,the more the omniscient power is overturned
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:24.03,Translation,,0,0,0,,and peels away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:28.27,Translation,,0,0,0,,to reveal an “engineered miracle”—
